Psalms__112.1: Praise the Lord, ye children: praise ye the name of the Lord.
Psalms__112.2: Blessed be the name of the Lord, from henceforth now and for ever.
Psalms__112.3: From the rising of the sun unto the going down of the same, the name of the Lord is worthy of praise.
Psalms__112.4: The Lord is high above all nations; and his glory above the heavens.
Psalms__112.5: Who is as the Lord our God, who dwelleth on high:
Psalms__112.6: And looketh down on the low things in heaven and in earth?
Psalms__112.7: Raising up the needy from the earth, and lifting up the poor out of the dunghill:
Psalms__112.8: That he may place him with princes, with the princes of his people.
Psalms__112.9: Who maketh a barren woman to dwell in a house, the joyful mother of children.
